# 301 Redirects — First Sight Films
# Order matters: first match wins. Keep specific rules + asset protections ABOVE wildcards.
# 301! forces the redirect even when a static file exists at that path.

# Domain canonicalization (2026-07-08): collapse the bare-domain chain to ONE hop.
# Before: http://firstsightfilms.com -> https://firstsightfilms.com -> https://www... (2 hops)
# Domain-level rules must sit above all path rules.
